- C2 ignore entries for `from weave.shared import refs_internal` point at weave.shared.refs_internal (submodule), not weave.shared.
- The prek hook must stay language:system so uv run uses the project env (grimp imports real weave).
- tests/ is OUTSIDE root_package weave -- test-side cross-imports are invisible to the guard by design until cutover.

